@startuml loginSequenceDiagram_2
actor User
participant "React Frontend" as FE
participant "Ory Oathkeeper" as Oathkeeper
participant "Ory Kratos" as Kratos
participant "Spring Boot Backend" as BE

== Login Flow Initialization ==

FE -> Oathkeeper : GET auth.irboard.local/self-service/login/browser\n+ Accept: application/json\n[rule: kratos-self-service-pass\nauthenticator: noop → allow]
Oathkeeper -> Kratos : GET /self-service/login/browser\n(passed through, noop auth)
Kratos --> Oathkeeper : 200 OK\n{ id: flowId,\n  ui: { nodes: [{ attributes:\n    { name: csrf_token, value: ... } }] } }
Oathkeeper --> FE : 200 OK\n{ id: flowId, ui: { nodes: [...] } }

note over FE : Store flowId and\nextract csrf_token from ui.nodes

==  ==

@enduml